<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11254</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>美罗城地铁站里，人们脚步匆匆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“让开!”一个男人说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我上班要迟到了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个年轻女人走进地铁站。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她背着小提琴，拿着帽子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把帽子放在地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，她开始拉小提琴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奇怪的音乐在空中响起。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所有人都停下脚步。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们全都看向那个年轻女人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55741</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，他们掏出钱包，扔到了帽子里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55741</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60851</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我等不及音乐会开始了。”玛拉说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60851</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65851</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“能听到真正的管弦乐真是太棒了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65851</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70841</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西和朋友们在美罗城公园里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70841</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>美罗城交响乐团将要在这里举行一场音乐会。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77453</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81703</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>人们在草地上铺上毯子坐着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81703</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>音乐家们在舞台上调试乐器。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天天气真暖和。”玛拉说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94424</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“温度会影响乐器。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94424</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98403</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以音乐家们要检查。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98403</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很喜欢现场音乐。”特勒尔说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107237</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“说不定明年我就能进学校的爵士乐队。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107237</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110135</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我一直在学单簧管。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110135</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114561</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克耸耸肩。“音乐会应该不错。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114561</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118619</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不过我不怎么喜欢古典音乐。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118619</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123868</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我喜欢摇滚乐！”杰克跳起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123868</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127994</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他两手举起来好像抱着吉他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127994</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134495</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家看到杰克装摇滚歌手跳舞，都笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134495</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯……我喜欢古典音乐。”玛拉说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“管弦乐队今天将演奏我最喜欢的歌曲。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我正在学习用大提琴演奏它，但是真的好难。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152218</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“只要你一直练习。”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158469</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你会拉得越来越好的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162260</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>说不定有一天你也能在这里表演。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162260</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167204</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛拉笑了。“我好像不行。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167204</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道一个人可能非常擅长音乐。”特勒尔说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西转了一下眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯……特勒尔。我怀疑火箭女孩儿会不会乐器。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔看起来很吃惊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你怎么知道我说的是火箭女孩儿？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190204</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190204</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“特勒尔，你总是提到火箭女孩儿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199701</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，罗西的手表响了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199701</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203957</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西看看周围，又看看她的朋友们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203957</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很快就回来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210666</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我……嗯……好像看到我家邻居了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210666</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我想去打个招呼。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218355</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西躲在雕像后，按了一下手表的按钮。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218355</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222053</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布洛姆市长的脸出现在屏幕上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有什么事吗，市长？”罗西问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们需要你的帮助，火箭女孩儿。”布洛姆市长说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“邦恩太太办了一个花园派对。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236301</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所有客人都被抢劫了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239552</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别担心，市长！”罗西说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239552</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我马上到！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>